{"type": "article", "id": 7836, "title": "Lanvin 可能要从它的台湾大股东那里转手", "description": "据说有部分中国买家已经出手", "date": "2015-03-27T08:40:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 1530, "name": "Lanvin"}, {"id": 8268, "name": "王效兰"}], "category": 19, "author": 75588, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 18, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606061454524uaD1rCxZqI3LETl.png", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t据 <span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\"><a href=\"http://wwd.com/markets-news/designer-luxury/lanvin-could-be-on-block-10100911/\" target=\"_blank\">WWD</a> </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">消息，拥有 </span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">75% Lanvin </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">股权的王效兰女士最近有意向转手。王效兰是台湾联合报业的发行人，</span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">2001 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">年从欧莱雅手中接下了经营不善的 </span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">Lanvin</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，很快委任原先在 </span><span style=\"font-family:Calibri;\">YSL </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">担任首席设计师的 </span>Alber Elbaz 自由发挥，并亲自负责品牌在亚洲的市场。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t2007 <span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">年，王效兰将 </span><span style=\"font-family:Arial;\">Lanvin </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">的香水和化妆品业务以 </span><span style=\"font-family:Arial;\">2200 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">万欧元的价格出售给香水代理制造商 </span>Inter Parfums 集团，说是需要资金来发展成衣线。之后，Lanvin <span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">确实重振了风采，先有奥巴马夫人被拍到穿了 </span><span style=\"font-family:Arial;\">Lanvin </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">的运动鞋，然后</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">在佛罗里达州开了全美第一家精品店，</span><span style=\"font-family:Arial;\">2010 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">年， </span><span style=\"font-family:Arial;\">Lanvin </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">还和 </span><span style=\"font-family:Arial;\">H&amp;M </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">合作推出秋冬系列招致疯抢。现在，</span><span style=\"font-family:Arial;\">L</span>anvin <span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">的年销售额可达到 </span><span style=\"font-family:Arial;\">2.5 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">亿欧元左右</span>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t近期，王效兰女士似乎已经对 <span style=\"font-family:Arial;\">Lanvin </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">“放任不管”，不太愿意投入大量资金来发展</span><span style=\"font-family:Arial;\"> Lanvin </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">的品牌管理和零售网络。一位不愿透露姓名的知情人对 </span><span style=\"font-family:Arial;\">WWD </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">表示，“情况比较复杂，不过今年应该就会有明确的消息出来”。据说过去几年一直都有买家表示过收购的意向，但王效兰并没有回应。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t回忆 <span style=\"font-family:Arial;\">Lanvin </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">品牌历史，几经转手，</span><span style=\"font-family:Arial;\">1989 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">年前一直都由 </span><span style=\"font-family:Arial;\">Lanvin </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">家族内经营管理。后由英国 </span><span style=\"font-family:Arial;\">Bernard </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">银行接手一年，很快抛给路易威登家族创立的 </span><span style=\"font-family:Arial;\">Orcofi</span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">，</span><span style=\"font-family:Arial;\">1994 </span><span style=\"font-family:宋体;\">年开始陆续被欧莱雅集团收购，直至王效兰接手，不知道下家又会给品牌带来什么。</span>\r\n</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\">\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}